what_worked: Applied decorrelate, date_cte_isolate, dimension_cte_isolate: Replaced double EXCEPT with pre-filtered dimension CTEs and NOT EXISTS anti-joins. Base customer/date combinations are computed once from store_sales, then correlated filters check for absence in catalog and web sales.
why_it_worked: Correlated subqueries re-execute per outer row; converting to JOIN eliminates per-row overhead; Pre-filtering date dimension into CTE reduces hash join probe table from 73K to ~365 rows; Pre-filtering all dimension tables into CTEs avoids repeated full-table scans
